🧑‍🎓 Student & Course creation

📌 Register students to courses with capacity validation and waitlisting

❌ Drop students from courses and promote waitlisted ones

📋 List enrolled students (sorted by name)

🔎 Search students by branch

📊 View courses sorted by enrollment or filter by instructor/credits

/src
 ├── model/
 │    ├── Student.java
 │    └── Course.java
 ├── service/
 │    └── RegistrationSystem.java
 └── main/
      └── Main.java

--- University Course Registration System ---
1. Register student to course
2. Drop student from course
3. List students in a course
4. List students by branch
5. List all courses sorted by enrollment
6. Filter courses by instructor
7. Exit
